and I promise <i>I'll</i> cooperate.

15:44.400 --> 15:47.529
Since when did we start
stocking the house with alcohol?

15:47.600 --> 15:50.171
You've been sober for 16 years.

15:50.200 --> 15:52.567
I think we're safe.

15:52.640 --> 15:55.564
Besides, we can't all
get high on Diet Coke.

15:58.920 --> 16:01.491
You remember
our first legislature run?

16:03.480 --> 16:08.520
Planting posters at 2:00 a.m.
On the median of Highway 90?

16:08.600 --> 16:10.409
Two kids,
fresh out of law school.

16:10.480 --> 16:12.766
Colin...

16:16.680 --> 16:19.206
I want you to see
someone with me.

16:19.280 --> 16:23.444
I know you don't want to,
but we don't have a choice.

16:26.000 --> 16:27.889
Did you have a choice

16:27.920 --> 16:31.129
when you slept with that
27-year-old cheerleader coach?

16:36.120 --> 16:37.239
Frank told you.

16:37.240 --> 16:39.641
Who fucking cares who told me?

16:39.720 --> 16:42.210
I'm sorry.

16:50.040 --> 16:54.011
I was trying, Deb.
