16:54.080 --> 16:55.889
Do you expect me
to congratulate you

16:55.960 --> 16:58.566
because you tried to keep
your dick in your pants?

16:59.880 --> 17:01.848
What is it you want to hear?

17:01.920 --> 17:06.323
That I'm fine you keep risking
everything we've worked for?

17:09.920 --> 17:13.288
Not everything
is about our career.

17:15.240 --> 17:17.242
I wish that were true.

17:30.200 --> 17:34.683
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

17:36.840 --> 17:39.605
All right, good job, girls.
